WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.469
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.469 --> 00:00:03.613
I'm excited to be with y'all again today.

00:00:03.613 --> 00:00:05.192
I have a word for you.

00:00:05.528 --> 00:00:10.860
This word is quite a bit; I don't know, I'll probably make it a two-part series here again.

00:00:10.860 --> 00:00:12.866
But I was praying.

00:00:13.666 --> 00:00:17.754
First off, I want to say this: I hope you had a Merry Christmas.

00:00:17.754 --> 00:00:19.440
I hope you had good family time.

00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:21.794
I hope you got your heart's desires.

00:00:21.794 --> 00:00:27.223
You know, it's a wonderful time of the year; God is so faithful.

00:00:28.149 --> 00:00:39.153
I was praying on Christmas night, and the Lord said, 'I want you to get inside the car, and I want you to drive around and pray.

00:00:39.153 --> 00:00:47.978
' So I got in the car—it was about five in the morning—and he said, 'I want you to listen to the song Prayer by Petra, the band Petra.

00:00:49.436 --> 00:00:51.536
I want you to listen to it in prayer.

00:00:51.536 --> 00:01:04.253
' So I just put it on repeat and just kept praying in the spirit and listening to Prayer by Petra and just driving around in my town.

00:01:04.747 --> 00:01:13.119
All of a sudden, the Lord just opened my eyes to the spirit realm when I was worshiping and singing and praying.

00:01:13.375 --> 00:01:17.504
I came home, and the Lord said, 'I want you to pray with your wife.

00:01:17.504 --> 00:01:22.160
' So I told my wife, 'We're going to pray, and we need to pray together.

00:01:22.160 --> 00:01:32.791
' So I started interceding, and the Lord showed me, just like he always does, the calendars; he shows me in visions things that are coming.

00:01:33.967 --> 00:01:40.405
In this one, I could see into January really clearly.

00:01:55.873 --> 00:01:56.105
I could see into February and March.

00:01:56.105 --> 00:02:18.480
I could see plots and plans of the wicked—of them plotting things against the American people, against America's elections, against a lot of things, interference.

00:02:21.320 --> 00:03:00.226
I have to be careful with some of it because I'm not going to release all of that, but I'm going to say it like this: I heard the Spirit of the Lord say, 'Great grace will be poured out over 2024—a great grace.

00:03:00.226 --> 00:03:02.546
' I saw a grace wave.

00:03:10.083 --> 00:03:27.739
I could see it on January, February, March, April, and May; there was an acceleration of great grace.

00:03:39.210 --> 00:03:54.235
I saw a change in the spiritual atmosphere concerning finances—a supernatural outpouring of finances for the people who are listening in the Body of Christ.

00:03:54.235 --> 00:04:01.360
It's going to pour on the just and the unjust.

00:04:03.777 --> 00:04:09.228
I saw a great wave of money in 2024.

00:04:11.545 --> 00:04:18.480
I saw a diffusing of another plot of a virus—a diffusing.

00:04:18.480 --> 00:04:52.040
Now, I don't understand that, but it was like it was going to try to be something that turned into nothing more so than what the enemy was trying to in store for 2024.

00:05:02.600 --> 00:05:03.080
It was like you let out a balloon.

00:05:04.520 --> 00:05:10.199
I saw going into April even more of a grace acceleration of finances.

00:05:10.199 --> 00:05:30.942
There was something about praying over April, and I could hear the Lord Jesus Christ talking to me when I was praying and singing.

00:05:30.942 --> 00:05:35.365
He was over this great grace time.

00:05:36.649 --> 00:05:39.493
I could see he was anticipating something.

00:05:39.493 --> 00:05:48.026
He was watching over America; I could see him watching over our land.

00:05:48.026 --> 00:06:05.767
He was looking at us with anticipation, watching how we were going to handle these finances, how we were handling this window of a grace explosion—what I'm going to call grace acceleration.

00:06:24.893 --> 00:06:25.639
I got clear into...

00:06:34.377 --> 00:06:34.826
I could see the weather.

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:47.760
I could see storms.

00:06:50.911 --> 00:06:57.876
I could see, as far as spring goes, a normal spring with an acceleration of long-track tornadoes.

00:07:00.690 --> 00:07:01.795
I saw the jet stream strengthening and accelerating.

00:07:01.795 --> 00:07:10.330
I'm not a meteorologist, so I'm just telling you what I see.

00:07:11.999 --> 00:07:31.891
I saw that the storms would be long-track tornadoes in some places that would be at a stronger category than an EF5 that we've never seen before.

00:07:31.891 --> 00:07:50.899
This is stuff that doesn't necessarily have to happen; this is stuff that we can pray over to stop.

00:07:50.899 --> 00:08:25.720
Because I'm a prophetic intercessor, I'm trying to tell you things that the Lord shows me that we have authority over, that we can change through the power of prayer.

00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:29.524
Over the storms, we have authority.

00:08:29.524 --> 00:08:41.159
We are able to speak to the storms and tell them, 'Peace, be still.

00:08:41.159 --> 00:09:20.772
' When he's showing me about the long-track tornadoes and these major events of the jet stream speeding up, I don't understand all that, but I'm just telling you we have authority over the storms and drought in major places.

00:09:20.772 --> 00:09:46.440
So, speak over the rain, speaking to the rain to come over your area so that you have water for your land; it doesn't have to be that way.

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:48.573
Going into...

00:09:53.694 --> 00:09:58.994
I saw Trump with major rallies, with seas of people coming to his rallies.

00:10:03.760 --> 00:10:14.744
I saw him speaking on a stage with a white shirt, a red tie, and a blue suit like he always wears.

00:10:15.959 --> 00:10:25.440
He was preaching, and what looked like mountains were in the background.

00:10:39.940 --> 00:10:40.410
I don't know where it was—maybe it was Arizona—but there were mountains on the horizon.

00:10:51.240 --> 00:10:54.172
I could see them, and he was speaking there.

00:11:08.537 --> 00:11:09.982
I won't tell you what I saw trying to happen against him; we just need to pray for his protection.

00:11:09.982 --> 00:11:13.279
That's all I will say.

00:11:13.279 --> 00:11:20.226
You will need to pray for his protection in massive rallies.

00:11:23.427 --> 00:11:25.267
I saw it outdoors, a big crowd and mountains.

00:11:25.267 --> 00:11:36.617
Going into 2025 again, I saw something like the great Hoover Dam in the Las Vegas, Nevada area.

00:11:36.617 --> 00:11:50.000
This was like a massive, thick, slate wall of something that looked as dark as onyx.

00:11:50.000 --> 00:11:58.480
Again, I saw it at the end of December going into January.

00:11:58.480 --> 00:12:01.800
It looked like it was impenetrable.

00:12:07.600 --> 00:12:07.800
The blackness was the darkest black I've ever seen before.

00:12:07.800 --> 00:12:20.010
It went up on a wall like this, and you could not see through it.

00:12:39.700 --> 00:12:46.479
It was like crude oil behind it.

00:12:47.199 --> 00:13:03.569
The more I was looking into January, February, March, and April, all of a sudden it split.

00:13:03.569 --> 00:13:21.289
What was blackest through those months had a bit of a green start to come upon the grass.

00:13:21.289 --> 00:13:40.680
There were some trees I could see, but then there was thick, thick black all on top of these trees in March, April, and May of 2025.

00:13:40.680 --> 00:13:57.244
I kept focusing on it because I was like, 'Lord, why am I seeing this darkness all on this timeframe?

00:13:57.244 --> 00:14:05.480
' But I saw Trump crying, hearing the word 'depression'—a Great Depression.

00:14:05.480 --> 00:14:13.920
Then I saw Trump in the Oval Office, and he was crying.

00:14:13.920 --> 00:14:24.777
He had his hands down on his head at his desk in the Oval Office.

00:14:29.714 --> 00:14:30.040
This is another thing we should pray over.

00:14:30.040 --> 00:14:39.503
I'm not trying to get political; I'm just telling you what I saw.

00:14:39.503 --> 00:14:44.420
He was crying and asking for mercy.

00:14:44.420 --> 00:14:56.120
He was crying out for mercy concerning America, and he was interceding.

00:15:09.135 --> 00:15:09.887
But it was a different type of Trump: he was skinnier, for one, and he looked worn out, per se.

00:15:16.729 --> 00:15:18.751
But he was broken to the point where he was interceding.

00:15:28.887 --> 00:15:31.295
All of a sudden, I saw pastors in the Oval Office with him, walking around praying.

00:15:31.295 --> 00:16:01.140
He had called for people to pray with him, and I could see these men—they weren't just standing there behind him like I've seen in pictures before; they were actually pacing and interceding in the Oval Office, praying in the spirit.

00:16:07.171 --> 00:16:10.959
I saw a man—I believe he's a pastor from somewhere—who had a bald head and hair on the sides.

00:16:10.959 --> 00:16:20.960
He was a tall man, very slender in my opinion—probably 240 or 250 pounds.

00:16:30.834 --> 00:16:31.079
He was walking back and forth praying, wearing a gray suit, a white shirt, and no tie.

00:16:31.079 --> 00:16:36.480
He was praying in there with Holy Ghost energy.

00:16:36.853 --> 00:16:46.920
The tears were just flowing down his face when he was interceding for the nation.

00:16:46.920 --> 00:16:51.560
All of a sudden, I saw something very interesting.

00:17:04.380 --> 00:17:04.711
You know the paddles you use to shock somebody to wake them up?

00:17:04.711 --> 00:17:10.679
I saw those hit the nation of America.

00:17:13.614 --> 00:17:16.479
I saw shockwaves go over the land, pulses.

00:17:16.479 --> 00:17:27.666
I could see the shocks again—boom—and I could see it rippling across the land.

00:17:27.666 --> 00:17:31.697
All of that black started to move.

00:17:35.246 --> 00:17:48.649
There was a thick black that started looking like waves of energy moving across the soil of America as this prayer was going on in the White House.

00:17:48.649 --> 00:17:54.475
Then all of a sudden, the Lord said, 'Look.

00:17:54.475 --> 00:18:09.080
' I saw toward the North Pole, and I saw a light that looked like a match.

00:18:09.960 --> 00:18:18.341
All of a sudden, the black was all over the world at this time.

00:18:18.341 --> 00:18:39.258
If you were to take an egg and put pressure from the inside out, like a chick breaking forth—that's the way this dome, which was a half-sphere over this area, was breaking.

00:18:40.236 --> 00:18:55.114
The light was like a match, and all of a sudden this energy—Holy Ghost energy—took it and exploded that blackness off.

00:18:55.114 --> 00:19:02.645
It started to fall in pieces like an eggshell shattering.

00:19:15.697 --> 00:19:15.983
All of a sudden, that anointing, that glow, that light from this match...

00:19:22.057 --> 00:19:26.440
it was the most intense light I've ever seen, similar to what's at the Father's throne.

00:19:26.440 --> 00:19:40.440
It was at a center, but there was light upon light around it from the north.

00:19:40.440 --> 00:19:58.413
It split this black out and exploded, and all of a sudden that light started sending rays of light through that eggshell-looking thing—this membrane, I'll call it.

00:20:12.144 --> 00:20:12.528
It started to split, and the light started shining all through it.

00:20:12.528 --> 00:20:19.440
Then the light started to spread.

00:20:19.440 --> 00:20:31.840
I couldn't figure out what that was, but that's what I saw when I was praying.

00:20:37.896 --> 00:20:38.159
It was quite beautiful.

00:20:51.039 --> 00:20:51.279
But the Black Dome was towards the north, by Ireland—that area is where this was at.

00:20:51.279 --> 00:20:57.462
Then I was taken back to 2024 instead of 2025.

00:20:57.462 --> 00:21:03.330
I'm interceding, so I want you all to pray with me.

00:21:03.330 --> 00:21:10.564
I'm not saying who the next president will be; I'm just telling you what I saw.

00:21:11.419 --> 00:21:17.040
I see in part, and I hear in part.

00:21:17.040 --> 00:21:32.022
I'm a prophetic intercessor, so I'm asking you to pray for the protection of 45, pray for this nation to turn around.

00:21:34.531 --> 00:21:41.349
I didn't see what happened after those shockwaves; the vision was cut off.

00:21:47.124 --> 00:21:47.355
I believe he's giving us more time here.

00:21:51.312 --> 00:21:59.520
I believe he's wanting to have a major revival and a major outpouring of his Spirit upon America and the earth.

00:22:01.884 --> 00:22:10.295
I told you I saw a major shaking coming and major events taking place throughout the world.

00:22:13.140 --> 00:22:17.319
I want to encourage you to intercede for this stuff.

00:22:17.319 --> 00:22:23.140
2024 is going to be a good year.

00:22:23.140 --> 00:22:30.793
There's going to be bad, yes, but it's what you focus on.

00:22:30.793 --> 00:22:37.040
There's going to be a great grace over 2024.

00:22:37.040 --> 00:22:39.057
There's hope.

00:22:39.057 --> 00:22:44.254
It's not all doom and gloom.

00:22:44.254 --> 00:22:55.840
There's hope for you and your household, for healing, for deliverance, for your children to have a good future.

00:22:55.840 --> 00:23:07.440
We have authority in this earth; we can pray over things and call those things that be not as though they were.

00:23:17.869 --> 00:23:18.194
You can be full of the joy of the Lord and have increase in your life.

00:23:18.194 --> 00:23:29.246
Listen to what the Spirit of the Lord is telling you to do on a daily basis.

00:23:29.246 --> 00:23:34.500
Pray without ceasing by having communion.

00:23:34.500 --> 00:23:44.200
Your heart towards him: 'Father, I seek your face, I need you for my direction.

00:23:44.200 --> 00:23:47.840
' He will teach you all things.

00:23:47.840 --> 00:23:55.148
He'll show you how to cook; he'll teach you about everything.

00:23:55.148 --> 00:23:59.640
He's an ever-present help in a time of need.

00:23:59.640 --> 00:24:07.106
If you build a relationship with him, he'll talk to you about everything.

00:24:07.106 --> 00:24:14.614
Some people think I should not make so many videos, so I prayed about it.

00:24:18.576 --> 00:24:32.919
The Lord said, 'Brandon, if Kenneth Hagin could preach a five-week revival twice a day and never get tired, you're fine to do a 15-minute sermon every several days.

00:24:32.919 --> 00:24:41.759
' He started laughing about it because people have such a small-minded mentality.

00:24:41.759 --> 00:24:52.080
You're never going to run out of the river if you're close to the Vine.

00:24:52.080 --> 00:25:02.740
If ye abide in me and my words abide in you, you shall ask what you will.

00:25:02.740 --> 00:25:12.919
I just want to be next to the living water.

00:25:12.919 --> 00:25:26.284
I didn't come on here to promote my channel; I came to preach to whoever will listen.

00:25:34.780 --> 00:25:35.110
I don't need 100,000 views to feel like I've done something.

00:25:35.110 --> 00:25:44.783
If five people get their lives touched, then I've done something.

00:25:49.790 --> 00:25:54.089
I was a janitor for 15 years; any kind of attraction is good.

00:25:54.364 --> 00:25:56.290
Jesus is using me, and I'm excited about it.

00:25:56.290 --> 00:26:08.880
All I want is for the Father to say, 'Well done, thy good and faithful servant.

00:26:08.880 --> 00:26:16.788
' I'm not about promotion from man; I need Jesus.

00:26:16.788 --> 00:26:23.480
If I'm abiding in him, he's in control.

00:26:23.480 --> 00:26:28.971
He's the captain of my ship.

00:26:28.971 --> 00:26:34.571
He is the Potter, and I'm the clay.

00:26:45.810 --> 00:26:46.148
I have this treasure in an earthen vessel.

00:26:46.148 --> 00:26:51.893
I'm about done with collaborations; it's a distraction.

00:27:03.283 --> 00:27:03.466
I hope that blesses you all today.

00:27:03.466 --> 00:27:10.813
I'm sorry if you hear my little girl in the background.

00:27:10.813 --> 00:27:15.619
Megan's overcoming autism, and she makes noises.

00:27:15.619 --> 00:27:21.000
I'm trying to make the video as best I can.

00:27:21.000 --> 00:27:27.702
She needs a healing, so I'm just being real with y'all.

00:27:27.702 --> 00:27:44.154
It's cold to go into my garage and do these videos, but I'd rather do them in my house because it's warmer in here.

00:27:44.154 --> 00:27:47.240
Let me pray for you.

00:27:47.240 --> 00:27:59.693
Father, I thank you for every single person who is listening.

00:28:15.780 --> 00:28:16.010
I pray blessing over them and increase over their houses.

00:28:16.696 --> 00:28:21.045
I call their marriages and children to be blessed.

00:28:22.819 --> 00:28:24.389
I call their bodies healed and whole.

00:28:24.389 --> 00:28:28.709
No weapon formed against them will prosper.

00:28:28.709 --> 00:28:42.279
We call them delivered from any kind of addictions—from chemicals to drugs to pornographies to abuses.

00:28:42.279 --> 00:28:48.500
We call them delivered in the name of Jesus.

00:28:48.500 --> 00:29:01.577
We thank you, Father, that they'll renew their minds and everything is going to be okay.

00:29:01.919 --> 00:29:09.479
I call blessing and increase, and I curse cancers, diabetes, heart disease, and sickness.

00:29:09.479 --> 00:29:17.039
Jesus paid the price for you to have all the healing you need.

00:29:17.759 --> 00:29:20.831
I call you healed, spirit, soul, and body.

00:29:36.200 --> 00:29:36.430
I call you delivered, sir, of PTSD.

00:29:37.349 --> 00:29:40.674
I command that tormenting spirit to go.

00:29:41.896 --> 00:29:47.627
I call for new kidneys in 2024; no more kidney or liver problems.

00:29:47.627 --> 00:29:51.450
I call your heart healed and whole.

00:29:51.450 --> 00:29:59.160
I speak to arteries in the neck—from clogged, blocked main arteries.

00:30:08.740 --> 00:30:09.016
No strokes.

00:30:11.639 --> 00:30:16.795
I speak healing over paralysis in the face or arms from strokes.

00:30:16.795 --> 00:30:21.090
Sometimes miracles are a process.

00:30:21.090 --> 00:30:26.644
Do not give up on the full manifestation.

00:30:33.780 --> 00:30:39.875
I don't give up on my daughter; I keep calling those things that be not as though they were.

00:30:39.875 --> 00:30:49.240
I call her healed all the time, and I'm seeing results.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
God is faithful.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
So believe for the full manifestation.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Move your fingers; move by faith.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Faith without works is dead.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
I believe with you for complete manifestations for every single one of you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Jesus came and set the captives free.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
He died and rose again for you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Today is your day for deliverance.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Give your heart to Jesus Christ today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Turn from your sin, and Jesus will set you free.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Jesus loves you so much.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
We will see you next time.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Have a blessed day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
